6. Have One Thoughtful Point of View

Product heads often remember candidates with a perspective.

You could say:

> "One area I'm particularly interested in is how AI and Open Banking converge. As customers authorize access to more financial data, the differentiation will shift from data access itself to intelligence generated from that data. The winners will be firms that combine secure data sharing with actionable insights while maintaining customer trust."



That statement connects your AI background directly to the future of Open Banking.

